text: Thomas Cullinan (14 June 1946 - 24 January 2010) was a South African cricketer who played in four first-class matches for North Eastern Transvaal in the 1968/69 season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1946 births Category:2010 deaths Category:South African cricketers Category:Northerns cricketers Category:Place of birth missing
